There are numerous artists with this name, including: 
1) Polynesian reggae/hip-hop/R&B artist George “Fiji” Veikoso (died 2025); 
2) a Danish metal band from København/Slagelse, Sjælland;  
3) a Swiss electro band located in Berne; 
4) a Russian electronic musician; 
5) a project from The Kills lead singer Jamie Hince; 
6) a female rapper. 

