There are multiple artists that are using the name "Soran";

1)  SORAN, not noisy like their name(SORAN in Korean means commotion/disturbance) but shows elegant and emotional pop/modern rock sound.In 2009, set their 4-men line-up and started their band.

They released their first EP [Why didn’t I get at that time?] in August 2010, and were chosen ‘Best Artist’ at the Grand Mint Festival 2013 among 70 artists. Their first album [natural]  was released and caught listeners’ interests with lyrics about normal daily life.  <a href="https://www.last.fm/music/Soran">Read more on Last.fm</a>
